graph TD
    A[Teams Integration Creation] --> B[OAuth Token Exchange]
    B --> C[Create Graph Subscription]
    C --> D[Store in Metadata]
    
    E[Cron Job - Every 15 min] --> F[Check All Teams Integrations]
    F --> G{Subscription Expiring?}
    G -->|Yes| H[Renew Subscription]
    G -->|No| I[Log Status]
    H --> J{Renewal Success?}
    J -->|Yes| K[Update Metadata]
    J -->|No| L[Create New Subscription]
    L --> K
    
    M[Integration Deletion] --> N[Delete Graph Subscription]
    N --> O[Cleanup Integration]